  case $(menu "Install" "ÓĹ≤  Package\nÔČ®  Web App\nÔíČ  TUI\nÔíá  Service\nÔā¨  Browser\nÓ≠≠  Utility\nÓĮŹ  Style\nůįĶģ  Development\nÔÖú  Editor\nÔíČ  Terminal\nůĪö§  AI\nÔĄõ  Gaming") in
